---
title: Hoisin Veggie Burgers with Beyond Meat® and Charred Jalapeño Mayo
description: Charring jalapeños adds a delicious smoky flavour profile and takes their heat down a notch. Add them to mayo and you've got a delicious zingy alternative to burger sauce that complements rich hoisin. There's extra sauce for dipping those wedges in, too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hoisin-veggie-burgers-b887c5f2.jpg
